    public ResponseEntity<ConvertedDatatablesData<LotoDetail>> LotoInfoesItemLotoDetailsThymeleafController.datatablesByIdsIn(@RequestParam("ids") List<Long> ids, DatatablesColumns datatablesColumns, GlobalSearch search, DatatablesPageable pageable, @RequestParam("draw") Integer draw) {
        
        Page<LotoDetail> lotoDetails = getLotoDetailService().findAllByIdsIn(ids, search, pageable);
        long totalLotoDetailsCount = lotoDetails.getTotalElements();
        ConvertedDatatablesData<LotoDetail> data =  new ConvertedDatatablesData<LotoDetail>(lotoDetails, totalLotoDetailsCount, draw, getConversionService(), datatablesColumns);
        return ResponseEntity.ok(data);
